data.description: Discover your very own country paradise in this stunning property, boasting an array of remarkable features. This charming home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a generous living space, and an inviting open-concept kitchen. The rear of the house reveals a delightful bonus room, complete with a wet bar, making it the ideal space for entertaining, a game room, or even a spacious home office. Notable upgrades include a tankless water heater and a water softener system, along with a comprehensive security camera system for your peace of mind.    Step into the fenced "backyard area" featuring a playground and a back porch with a hot tub, providing the perfect spot to unwind beneath the starry night sky.    The property showcases a substantial 30x40 outbuilding, currently configured as a well-appointed dog kennel. This climate-controlled kennel includes two mini-split systems, washer and dryer hookups, electricity, water, and a convenient floor drainage system for effortless maintenance.    Spanning a generous 7.5 acres, the property is fully enclosed with perimeter fencing and cross-fencing to accommodate animals. It offers an array of amenities, including a private pond stocked with tilapia, a playground, a fire pit, and a dedicated shooting berm, perfect for your private gun range. Additionally, a serene wooded area at the rear ensures privacy and space for exploration, while the cleared front area provides an ideal area for animals and various outdoor activities. This property truly encompasses all you could desire in your own tranquil haven.
